2023 Lunar New Year collaboration with @Carlsberg ~🐇🧧🍺 

The collaboration concept is built on the Chinese traditional value and wish for New Year Reunion, featuring the magical rabbits transmuted from the golden liquid of Carlsberg premium brew. The rabbits gather around in the beer forest and bring along with Happiness, Wellness, and Prosperity together.

Agency: Somxing
Creative Director: Isabelle Gavaalda
